      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARROW SWIFTY (2) is having her first look at this course. In the money last start when second (22.59) at Warrnambool over 390m. Must come into calculations. PAPA WHO (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing eighth (17.34) in a T3 Grade 6 at Healesville. Should be about the mark. BABY YOSHI (6) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (23.66) last time in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. A big run wouldn't surprise. ASTON PRESTON (8) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
